    {
      "id": "PopularPost165675",
      "post_content": "@tavaritz  \n  \nIf you block a war mammoth with three Drudge Skeletons, your opponent must assign lethal damage to each one before assigning damage to you due to trample. So your opponent has to assign one damage to each skeleton. You pay one mana to regenerate each one. No damage can be dealt to you. All of your skeletons live. The elephant dies. I don't see a problem.",
      "posted_by": "NeedADispenserHere",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost165675\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">@tavaritz<br/><br/>If you block a war mammoth with three Drudge Skeletons, your opponent must assign lethal damage to each one before assigning damage to you due to trample. So your opponent has to assign one damage to each skeleton. You pay one mana to regenerate each one. No damage can be dealt to you. All of your skeletons live. The elephant dies. I don't see a problem.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '165675'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy37055\">NeedADispenserHere</span>\r\n                                (6/2/2011 8:02:50 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Ima